<tr bgcolor="#7A7AA5"><td><b>Gladius Fatalis and Darkenbane merge!</b></td><td align="right"><b>20-09-2001</b></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2"><font size="1">Submitted by <a href="mailto:grayrage@darkenbane.com">Grayrage</a> on 20-09-2001 11:39</font><p>With the dismantling of the "Gray Pact", the leaderships of both DB and GF decided it would be best for event planning and execution to merge our forces.   Not all of the former GF are now DB, however, the core has moved over with Vega retaining leadership over his men (and women).<br>
<br>
During the planning stages of this merge there was nothing bad to be said by either groups.  After the actual change was made, everyone seemed to fit well.  It was a noticeable contrast, however, between the mercenary killers of DB and the more refined and upstanding Gladius Fatalas.  Most DB feel the conversion of the GF personell into ruthless and unrelenting killers will be quickly completed whilst the GF folks hope to introduce some class and refinement *cough* to the murdering scum known as....DarkenBane!<br>
<br>
Beware foes, as this day the Neutral Team hath grown stronger and Darkenbane stands at it's front with a knife to your throat!!<br>
<br>
