<tr bgcolor="#7A7AA5"><td><b>The "Gray Pact" Disbanded</b></td><td align="right"><b>17-09-2001</b></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="2"><font size="1">Submitted by <a href="mailto:grayrage@darkenbane.com">Grayrage</a> on 17-09-2001 13:51</font><p>After some careful thought, the "Gray Pact" is being disbanded as it was creating expectations among certain groups of individuals that were causing more troubles than not.<br>
<br>
Darkenbane will conduct their own PvE events, but will still come to the call of other Neutral Guilds for PvP defense of our lands.<br>
<br>
We have found that the lack of organized in game communication causes far to many problems in engaging in multi-guild PvE events.  We will NOT necessarily EXCLUDE people from our PvE, but for the most part such events will be DB only.<br><br></td></tr>
